item.title: Gah stupid errors
item.dc:creator: @Budda Budda
item.description:
@Budda wrote:

Omg. Idiots. Seriously.

The method you are using those things in, objectID, objectX and objectY, haven’t been declared, which brings me to the assumption that you are adding the things you want in the wrong area.
Either: Tell me what you’re trying to do, and I’ll try direct you to the right place,
Or: Declare what objectID, objectX and objectY are.
